events.name: Front End TL;DR February 2015
events.description: We are visiting PocketMath, a fast growing startup that bootstrapped itself to a juicy million investment round. Come find out how they tackle front end challenges like serving billions of impressions. FEDS TL;DR is all about hands-on learning. Make new friends and explore some intriguing bit of front end tech you always wanted to try. Satisfaction guaranteed. Schedule: Every third Monday of the month. Different venue each time. 7:00pm — Arrival, registration, seating 7:10pm — Intro talk 7:30pm — Teams work on mini challenges 8:30pm — Presentations, awards 9:00pm — The end. More info: http://feds.strikingly.com/ PS: Bring a laptop and show up a bit earlier to get set up on the wifi.
